<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q24_v8" title="Q24_v8" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>El área A(x) de un rectángulo, en unidades cuadradas, viene dada por la expresión
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo>
        <m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
        <m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
        <m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn>
      </m:math>.
      Si las longitudes de sus lados se expresan mediante binomios en x y se cumple que área = lado_largo · lado_corto, ¿cuál de las siguientes parejas de binomios podría corresponder a las longitudes de los lados del rectángulo?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <p>
          <m:math>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo>
            <m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:math>
        </p>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al multiplicar los binomios de esta opción se obtiene (x + 7)(x + 4) = x² + 4x + 7x + 28 = x² + 11x + 28, que no coincide con x² + 3x − 28.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <p>
          <m:math>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo>
            <m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:math>
        </p>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Al multiplicar los binomios se obtiene (x + 7)(x − 4) = x² − 4x + 7x − 28 = x² + 3x − 28, que coincide exactamente con el área dada.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <p>
          <m:math>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo>
            <m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:math>
        </p>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al multiplicar los binomios de esta opción se obtiene (x − 7)(x + 4) = x² + 4x − 7x − 28 = x² − 3x − 28, que no coincide con x² + 3x − 28.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <p>
          <m:math>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo>
            <m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:math>
        </p>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al multiplicar los binomios de esta opción se obtiene (x + 8)(x − 5) = x² − 5x + 8x − 40 = x² + 3x − 40, que no coincide con x² + 3x − 28.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la expresión del área</strong></p>
            <p>El área del rectángulo es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                <m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Como el área es el producto de las longitudes de los lados, debemos factorizar este trinomio.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Buscar dos números cuyo producto sea −28 y cuya suma sea 3</strong></p>
            <p>Probamos parejas de enteros que multiplicadas den −28:</p>
            <p>7 y −4, porque:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>y además:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces, el trinomio se factoriza como:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                <m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
                <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Verificar la multiplicación</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
                <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                <m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                <m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                <m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>La igualdad coincide exactamente con el área dada.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Comparar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>La pareja de binomios correspondiente es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo>
                <m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Eso corresponde a la alternativa B.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La respuesta correcta es <strong>ChoiceB</strong>, porque sus binomios multiplicados generan exactamente el área del rectángulo.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>